#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:11
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"ASTEROID_EXPLORE\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[1]/text"
msgstr "(Deconstructor) Attempt to mine the asteroids."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:13
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"ASTEROID_EXPLORE\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"You carefully extract as much usable material as possible from the nearest "
"asteroids while waiting for the FTL to charge."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:18
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"ASTEROID_EXPLORE\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/text"
msgstr "(RSA Mining Beam) Attempt to mine the asteroids."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:20
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"ASTEROID_EXPLORE\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"Your RSA Mining Beam is extremely effective at extracting material from the "
"asteroids. One swipe, and even the bigger asteroids crumble into pieces. "
"There's only one problem; you can't collect it all fast enough! In order to "
"collect it all, the Rebel fleet will probably have time to catch up."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:23
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"ASTEROID_EXPLORE\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Collect it, we need the scrap."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:25
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"ASTEROID_EXPLORE\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "You collect as much more as you can. Hopefully, it's worth it."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:31
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"ASTEROID_EXPLORE\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/event/choice[@req=\"MAGNET_ARM\"]/text"
msgstr "(Magnetic Arm) Use the arm to collect it quickly."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:33
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"ASTEROID_EXPLORE\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/event/choice[@req=\"MAGNET_ARM\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"With your magnetic arm, you are able to collect most of the rest in a timely"
" manner. Thanks electromagnetism!"

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:38
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"ASTEROID_EXPLORE\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Leave, we can't risk it."

#: src-en/data/events.xml.append:40
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"ASTEROID_EXPLORE\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"It pains you to leave perfectly usable scrap behind like this, but you can't"
" let the Rebels catch up. You prepare to jump."
